      <title>土耳其埃尔多安升级反以色列言论，威胁干预</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/turkey-s-erdogan-escalates-anti-israel-rhetoric-with-threat-of-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安正在升级其对以色列的言论，暗示土耳其可能会代表巴勒斯坦进行干预，可能还会提供军事支持，其方式类似于土耳其在其他冲突中所做的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/turkey-s-erdogan-escalates-anti-israel-rhetoric-with-threat-of-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 20:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚加息争论将随通胀数据升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-rate-hike-debate-set-to-crescendo-with-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[关于澳大利亚央行是否需要实施周期末期紧缩政策的争论很可能会在本周公布的季度通胀数据后得到解决 —— 而澳元也将受到波及。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/australia-rate-hike-debate-set-to-crescendo-with-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储在背后支持吗？债券交易员押注大幅降息以防万一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/is-the-fed-behind-bond-traders-bet-on-big-rate-cuts-just-in-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券交易员已经做好了从九月份开始逐步降息的准备，他们正在加大押注，以防美国经济突然下滑迫使美联储采取更激进的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/is-the-fed-behind-bond-traders-bet-on-big-rate-cuts-just-in-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚表示将根据经济改革计划实行货币浮动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/ethiopia-says-it-will-float-currency-under-economic-reform-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理阿比·艾哈迈德表示，作为正在进行的宏观经济改革的一部分，埃塞俄比亚计划实施货币比尔浮动政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/ethiopia-says-it-will-float-currency-under-economic-reform-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 16:27:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚超额死亡揭示新冠病毒的长而致命的尾巴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/excess-deaths-in-australia-reveal-covid-s-long-lethal-tail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚人的死亡率仍高于疫情之前，这反映出新冠病毒的持续影响可能导致全球死亡和疾病持续增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/excess-deaths-in-australia-reveal-covid-s-long-lethal-tail</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
